<p>Calculating the sum of squared deviations:</p>
<p><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="mrel">=</span></span><span class="base"><span class="mord">23.6025</span><span class="mbin">+</span></span><span class="base"><span class="mord">15.6025</span><span class="mbin">+</span></span><span class="base"><span class="mord">15.6025</span><span class="mbin">+</span></span><span class="base"><span class="mord">8.4025</span><span class="mbin">+</span></span><span class="base"><span class="mord">3.8025</span><span class="mbin">+</span></span><span class="base"><span class="mord">0.9025</span><span class="mbin">+</span></span><span class="base"><span class="mord">0.9025</span><span class="mbin">+</span></span><span class="base"><span class="mord">0.9025</span><span class="mbin">+</span></span><span class="base"><span class="mord">4.2025</span><span class="mbin">+</span></span><span class="base"><span class="mord">4.2025</span><span class="mbin">+</span></span><span class="base"><span class="mord">9.2025</span><span class="mbin">+</span></span><span class="base"><span class="mord">9.2025</span><span class="mbin">+</span></span><span class="base"><span class="mord">16.2025</span><span class="mbin">+</span></span><span class="base"><span class="mord">16.2025</span><span class="mbin">+</span></span><span class="base"><span class="mord">16.2025</span><span class="mbin">+</span></span><span class="base"><span class="mord">16.2025</span><span class="mbin">+</span></span><span class="base"><span class="mord">36.6025</span><span class="mbin">+</span></span><span class="base"><span class="mord">49.6025</span><span class="mbin">+</span></span><span class="base"><span class="mord">82.2025</span><span class="mbin">+</span></span><span class="base"><span class="mord">123.2025</span></span></span></span></span><br />
<span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml">=394.5</span></span></span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Now,<br />
calculate the <span style="text-decoration: underline;">variance</span>:</p>
<p>$$\sigma^2 = \frac{{394.5}}{{20}}$$</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span class="mord mathnormal"><span class="base">σ</span><sup>2</sup> = 19.725</span></p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Standard Deviation</span></p>
<p>The standard deviation <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml">σ</span></span> is the square root of the variance:</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"> <span class="mord mathnormal"><span class="base">σ</span></span> = √19.725 = 4.44</span></span></span></p>
<p><strong>Coefficient of Variation (CV)<br />
</strong>The coefficient of variation is calculated using the formula:<strong><br />
</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span class="base"><span class="mord mathnormal">CV = (σ / <span class="mord"><span class="mfrac"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist">μ) x</span></span></span></span></span> 100%</span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span class="base"><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal">CV = (4.44 / 5.95) x 100%<br />
CV = 74.67%</span></span></span></p>
<p>Hence,</p>
<ul style="list-style-type: square;">
<li>Mean: <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml">5.95</span></span></li>
<li>Median: <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml">8.5</span></span></li>
<li>Mode: <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml">5,10</span></span></li>
<li>Variance: <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml">19.725</span></span></li>
<li>Standard Deviation: <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml">≈4.44</span></span></li>
<li>Coefficient of Variation: <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml">≈74.67%</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
